{"type": "article", "id": 22403, "title": "爱马仕增长放缓，以及，最红水桶包品牌又出新系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-02-17T10:21:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3321, "name": "Stella McCartney"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 19775, "name": "Kylie Jenner"}, {"id": 3659, "name": "Oscar de la Renta"}, {"id": 2684, "name": "Mansur Gavriel"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 2909, "name": "Jeremy Scott"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 7397, "name": "MSGM"}, {"id": 2881, "name": "Vera Wang"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152834Kf9wdDcTM5rB4zRe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/2/stella-mccartney-menswear\">Stella McCartney 将推出首个男装系列</a>｜</b>知名伦敦设计师 Stella McCartney，最终确认了传言已久进军男装的举动， 将会在今年六月发布 2017 年春夏系列。而这并不是她首次涉足男装流域，早期，她的时尚事业开始于以传统西装定制闻名的萨维尔街，为 Edward Sexton 工作，直到 1997 年成为女装品牌 Chloé 的创意总监。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Puma-confirms-brand-ambassador-deal-with-Kylie-Jenner,657150.html#.VsPGZoRVfBI\">Puma 确认与 Kylie Jenner 签约</a>｜</b>上周美国媒体报道运动品牌 Puma 和 Kylie Jenner 将签合作协议。而昨日品牌在拉斯维加斯的 Agenda 贸易展上确认了这一消息，和卡戴珊家族最年轻的成员之一签下了七位数的合约，Kylie Jenner 将出现自 Puma 品牌营销活动以及个人的社交媒体露出。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1455664452106.html\">爱马仕增长放缓</a> | </b>爱马仕周三发布四季度及全年财报，该公司表示由于巴黎暴恐导致国内销售疲软，该集团四季度法国本土销售增幅仅为 1%。与此同时，爱马仕预警，由于全球经济及地缘政治不稳定和货币动荡，2016 年增幅可能将低于 8% 的中期目标，该公司此前目标为 10%。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/eyewear/jeremy-scott-italia-independent-sunglasses-10355116/\">Jeremy Scott 将合作推出墨镜</a> | </b>合作对象为 Italia Independent ，墨镜将在今年 6 月推出，售价大约为 160 美元。Italia Independent 曾与阿迪达斯达成 4 年合作协议，为旗下三叶草子牌生产眼镜，这家公司已经在米兰上市。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/msgm-to-ban-social-medias-at-show-in-milan-10354132/\">MSGM 呼吁前去看秀的媒体和观众不要使用社交媒体</a> | </b>时装秀邀请函上写着：“把你的手机放回去，请享受秀本身。”设计师 Massimo Giorgetti 也表示，他将不发布秀场图像，直到这个系列即将进店上架。他同时表示了对社交网络的一系列困惑。<br></p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/furla-revenues-accessories-market-10353425/\">Furla 2015 收益攀升 30%</a>｜</b>意大利包袋品牌 Furla 去年表现良好，截至 2015 年 12 月 31 日的 12 个月内获得了将近 30% 的收益增长，销售额达到了 3.39 亿欧元（约合 3.76 亿美元），而 2014 年同期则为 2.62 亿欧元（3.48 亿美元）。恒定汇率下，销售额也攀升了 25% 。</p>\n<p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>这里有一些纽约时装周上值得一看的秀场图：</p>\n<p class=\"\">Oscar de la Renta<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152810kMX9seu7bLZTOhN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Coach 1941<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152811vnCXFgopwVILjP0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"4.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Vera Wang<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152811jPLiTo4F8bHp13sc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.78703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Y-3 2016 春夏广告，具体视频点击<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ejBPLzEinE\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这里</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152812yK7xSf9NEz3e4Lkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152812jW0nqol1Ng3MaDXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">横竖抢不到的水桶包品牌 Mansur Gavriel 又出新系列，  这次的品类比较丰富，除了手提包、clutch bag 等手袋系列外，还推出了 5 款鞋履，包括芭蕾舞鞋、矮跟鞋、loafers 等。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152813hUJ6m7NtyivHOfrL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152813g0vXTt5ZIGxHuJD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152814N13TxPzWn7FMRGEd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152814dTvlr0Gps9L84I5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152815mculSEPHFJWxMZOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152815OkMYFuzBwaPm5CRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615281676O9NBpRYy0bVihc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152816KDiqOanUx3hXLwyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152817EyPtAFjIJzX9qZl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152817G4Esp9JRALSDIbKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152818WepABXrJM7FSGoT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Zara 2016 的春夏广告释出，这是年轻副线 TRF，以金银和色彩条纹最抢眼。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152818oPp4sCiDSEV1NOny.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061528197BToWjOL6wKDJRt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152819x41oZIW90rJiAYEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152820yUzopbXR4idAHqWn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152820gIBCxbv8J0qwF3XD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152821RtrK27GUmYEhM10s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152821QU8WrpSxgVLwG9zN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">每一次的时装周之后，T 台上模特们的妆容和发型都会被纷纷效仿。这里有一些这次纽约时装周上的有趣发型，比如辫子和马尾的不同编法。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061528229YoFuaBsXZNKiE7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061528227NW01st8o4gFZMOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061528237bpGk4cCt5yFLj8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152823jODW5BFMc6ZwSp0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152824balqBSLg8VjMyGzY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152824KeVrbLIF7sU1DXnc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152824wjOJPGFqa2ItVgUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152825zJu9BZlKm5cAE36X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615282592IXD7L56wMyAUTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>visvim 2016 秋冬预览，日式剪裁的 Cardigan、美式风格的配衬单品如 Bandana Skirt、Polo Shirt、Duffle Coat，加上浅色调及简约轮廓，充满休闲气息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152826zmf015Rwbh9WdKuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152826wVT4f9DBZkKcvaNC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152827A64c5FouXVzMt8vm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152827d9EvK8VgItF2sBhA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615282882REcl1tgMnODsrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152828ynA6co0PUKx3EfBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这里有一个 NBA 明星人物主题的邮票，包含了乔丹、詹姆斯·哈登、艾弗森、斯蒂芬·库里、科比、罗德曼、凯文·杜兰特，皮蓬和勒布朗·詹姆斯等。由 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BBk_vZXIny0/?taken-by=ilovedust\">ilovedust</a> 出品。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152829VhCDqrbemupt07vI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152829SgmZqn2VtvYkxocl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152830VeijD6pxl7cGrnNC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152830MU40Pqu9XFeLo5gR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152831eydaIqzPkQ7Dlt9v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152832HwZe2avKiJ8rq7o1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152832RA3rOgcIPDkwiE50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152832NQOF4MwlpcgjAIUi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152833GFzaQ8chsdlfKIxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}